sub_title: #1 Best-Selling Author | Award-Winning Entrepreneur | TEDx Speaker
summary:
Arian Adeli Koodehi is a young author, entrepreneur, and student. At a young age of 13, he started developing AI algorithms for virtual, self-driving cars, which marked the beginning of his entrepreneurial journey. Arian has since been involved in various startups in different industries such as FoodTech and FinTech. At 16, he published his first book, “The Quantified Fortune”, which simplifies modern finance for a young audience. At 18, Arian delivered his first TED talk on finding one's direction in life, drawing on his experience as a young entrepreneur. Today, Arian is focused on developing solutions in the media industry and helping other startups bring their visions to life.

You can visit him online at www.arianadeli.com.
